I have come home with only one goal--

7
00:00:10,100 --> 00:00:11,830
拯救我的城市
to save my city.

8
00:00:12,420 --> 00:00:15,830
但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手
But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.

9
