孝子

12
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:25,210
成為另一個存在
I must be something else.

13
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,340
《綠箭》前情回顧
Previously on "Arrow"...

14
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:29,990
這個人對我們沒用了
This one's no longer of use to us.

15
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:31,540
等一下  他或許還有用
Wait. He could still be useful.

16
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:34,100
她說得對  一旦我們殺了他的朋友
She's right. Once we get rid of his friends,

17
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:35,860
我們就得需要他帶我們去墓地了
we'll need him to lead us to the grave.

18
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:37,610
你要再回到島上
You're going back to the island.

19
00:00:38,490 --> 00:00:39,660
你已經失去你的父親了
Look, you already lost your dad.

20
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:40,910
你母親還在
Your mom, she's still here.

21
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:42,390
她一定很想見見你
And I'm sure she'd love to see you.

22
00:00:42,390 --> 00:00:44,340
我不會去監獄看她
I'm not going to that prison.

23
00:00:44,730 --> 00:00:46,500
我只知道這樣才能讓她痛苦
It's the only way I know how to hurt her.

24
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,220
我很想恨你
And I want to hate you.

25
00:00:49,260 --> 00:00:50,430
但是我恨不起來
But I can't.

26
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:55,140
我一直以為我們之間沒有秘密
I didn't think that there were secrets kept between us.

27
00:00:55,140 --> 00:00:57,690
媽媽  你在隱瞞什么
Mom...what are you hiding?

28
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:03,110
我是莫伊拉·迪爾登·奎恩
My name is Moira Dearden Queen.

29
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:06,480
我是奎恩聯合企業的代理執行總裁
I am the acting CEO of Queen Consolidated.

30
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:06,480
{\an8}半年前

31
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,430
上帝  請原諒我  我辜負了這座城市
And, god forgive me, I have failed this city.

32
00:01:11,050 --> 00:01:13,710
我被迫參與了一項事業
I have been complicit in an undertaking

33
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:15,780
它有一個恐怖的目的
with one horrible purpose--

34
00:01:19,970 --> 00:01:22,640
摧毀貧民區以及里面每一個人
to destroy the glades and everyone in it.

35
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,580
如果你住在貧民區
If you reside in the glades,

36
00:01:24,530 --> 00:01:28,360
{\an8}貧民區遭到攻擊

37
00:01:24,670 --> 00:01:26,970
請立刻離開
please, you need to get out now.

38
00:01:27,550 --> 00:01:30,610
你和你的孩子們  命懸一線
Your lives and the lives of your children depend on it.

39
00:01:31,860 --> 00:01:32,870
拜托了
Please.

40
00:01:33,580 --> 00:01:35,330
典獄長說我們得撤退了
Warden says we got to evacuate.

41
00:01:37,610 --> 00:01:38,810
幫我拿走這些
Help me get these out of here.

42
00:01:38,810 --> 00:01:41,390
-那囚犯呢  -不管他們
- What about the inmates? - Leave 'em.

43
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,000
-來  放我出去  -不
- Over here, let me out. - No.

44
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:35,150
-把鑰匙給我  -不不  你太暴力
- Give me the keys! - No, no, too violent.

45
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:37,840
-帶我走  -太邋遢  太愚蠢
- Take me! - Too sloppy, too stupid.

46
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:40,620
你太野心勃勃
Too...ambitious.

47
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,310
你
You.

48
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:44,600
我喜歡你的工作
I love your work.

49
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,450
很有前途
Big future.

50
00:02:47,550 --> 00:02:48,650
小心點
Hey, be careful.

51
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,010
可能會有余震
There's liable to be aftershocks.

52
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,800
我巴不得呢
Oh, I'm counting on it.

53
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:17,300
綠箭  第二季第七集

54
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:25,890
{\an8}現在

55
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:30,430
奎恩先生  您母親勝訴的幾率有多大
Mr. Queen, what are your mother's chances?

56
00:03:30,430 --> 00:03:32,270
是不是有人監視以防她自殺
Is she on suicide watch?

57
00:03:34,010 --> 00:03:35,810
奎恩先生  能發表評論嗎
Mr. Queen, can you give us any comment?

58
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:38,000
這不公平  又不是他們進行庭審
It's not fair. They're not the ones on trial.

59
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:39,220
那也不能阻止簡·洛林
That won't stop Jean Loring

60
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:41,670
用他們來獲取公眾的同情
from using them as props to drum up sympathy.

61
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:43,130
你看起來不大擔心
You don't seem overly concerned.

62
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:45,920
她在直播電視里承認自己是共犯
She confessed to being an accomplice on live television.

63
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:48,420
她也說了是馬爾科姆·梅林強迫的她
She also sad that Malcolm Merlyn coerced her.

64
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:51,320
你有什么證據  對吧
You have something, don't you?

65
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,180
我是你的合伙律師  亞當
I thought I was your co-counsel, Adam.

66
00:03:54,810 --> 00:03:55,690
如果你手里有王牌
If you're holding a trump card,

67
00:03:55,690 --> 00:03:57,590
難道不該和我分享一下嗎
don't you think maybe you should share it with me?

68
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:59,220
這場庭審會很棒的
It's going to be a good trial.

69
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,220
我們進去吧
Come on, let's get inside.

70
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:13,650
你沒必要這樣做
You don't have to do this.

71
00:04:13,650 --> 00:04:14,770
艾沃說有必要
Ivo says we do.

72
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:16,310
你的朋友們對他的人來說是個威脅
Your friends are a danger to his men.

73
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,880
快去  別驚動他們
Go. Quick and quiet.

74
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,130
斯萊德  莎朵  快跑
Slade! Shado! Run!

75
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,490
里面沒人
There's no one here.

76
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:38,680
他們肯定轉移了
They must have moved on from their position.

77
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:41,080
炸藥放好了  這是引爆器
Chargers are placed. Here's the detonator.

78
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,610
確保他們無"家"可歸
Make sure they have no place to return to.

79
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:45,710
去吧
Go.

80
00:04:46,210 --> 00:04:47,050
你
And you.

81
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,330
現在你要帶我們去墓地
Now you're going to take us to the graves.

82
00:04:50,650 --> 00:04:52,340
走吧  拉他起來
Let's go. Get him up.

83
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,530
動身
Let's get clear.

84
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:02,550
你找到引爆器了嗎
Did you find the detonator?

85
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:03,380
找到了
Yes.

86
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:07,990
我們真走運
We were lucky.

87
00:05:08,610 --> 00:05:11,250
是我走運  你很厲害
I was lucky. You were good.

88
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:13,080
不管怎樣
Either way...

89
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:15,090
奧利弗都在他們手上
they have Oliver.

90
00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:17,050
我去找他
I'm going after him.

91
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:18,960
我陪你去
Not alone.

92
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,730
你都沒法走路
You can barely walk.

93
00:05:23,110 --> 00:05:25,100
所以我更不能待在這里
All the more reason not to stay here.

94
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,710
不能再給他們一次把我炸飛的機會
Give them another chance at blowing me up.

95
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:35,930
你倆沒事吧
Are you two ok?

96
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:37,140
我該問你這個問題
I should be asking you that question.

97
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:38,180
我沒事
I'll be fine.

98
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,720
你看上去像得了流感
You look like you have the flu.

99
00:05:39,990 --> 00:05:40,790
如果真是那樣  我不該
If that's true, I shouldn't

100
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:42,460
浪費時間接種疫苗的
have wasted my time getting vaccinated.

101
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:44,920
狄格爾  不管是怎么回事  回家去吧
Diggle, whatever it is, just go home.

102
00:05:45,530 --> 00:05:47,300
奧利弗  我能處理好的  好嗎
Oliver, listen, I can take care of things. All right?

103
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:49,200
不  我們沒事的
No, we'll be fine, all right?

104
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,200
去休息吧  別逼我叫警察
Go rest. And don't make me call a cop.

105
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,900
這里就有幾個
There are a few of them around here.

106
00:06:20,050 --> 00:06:22,800
我被迫參與了一項事業
I have been complicit in an undertaking

107
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,010
它有一個恐怖的目的
with one horrible purpose--

108
00:06:25,490 --> 00:06:28,370
摧毀貧民區以及里面每一個人
to destroy the glades and everyone in it.

109
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:32,360
奏效了  貧民區被毀
And it worked. The Glades were destroyed.

110
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:34,350
哀橫遍野  人們流離失所
Homes and lives were lost.

111
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:36,530
都是因為她的行為
All because of her actions.

112
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,460
確實  她想清楚之后做了悔改
True, she had second thoughts;

113
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:42,100
自責促使她發表這份聲明
remorse which compelled her to deliver this statement.

114
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:44,580
但我想替那天逝去的503條生命
But on behalf of the 503 lives

115
00:06:44,580 --> 00:06:46,180
在這里說一句話
that were extinguished that day,

116
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:49,740
莫伊拉·奎恩  你的自責太遲了
I say, Moira Queen, your remorse comes too late.

117
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,110
在過去的五年里
For the last five years,

118
00:06:52,790 --> 00:06:54,180
我和我家人的生命
under the threat for my life

119
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:56,090
受到了威脅
and the lives of my family...

120
00:06:57,130 --> 00:06:59,260
為什么這些威脅沒有讓她沉默
Why wouldn't those threats silence her?

121
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:02,430
為什么莫伊拉·奎恩沒有被嚇倒
Why wouldn't Moira Queen be terrified?

122
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:05,230
馬爾科姆·梅林殺了她的第一任丈夫
Malcolm Merlyn killed her first husband,

123
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:06,550
綁架了她的第二任丈夫
abducted her second.

124
00:07:06,550 --> 00:07:08,610
她為什么不擔心自己的性命
Why wouldn't she be in fear for her life?

125
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:10,690
不擔心自己兒女的性命
For the lives of her children?

126
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,970
你們會怎么做
What would you do?

127
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,560
如果你們的子女
If it were your children in the crosshairs

128
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,250
被一個瘋子控制
of a mad man's rage?

129
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:23,690
星級實驗室的粒子加速器
They say the Star lab's particle accelerator

130
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:26,050
會如期開啟
will be turned on right on schedule.

131
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,900
其他新聞  我們剛剛收到消息
In other news, we have just received word

132
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:30,730
莫伊拉·奎恩庭審中的正反兩方
that both sides have now completed their opening statements

133
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:32,540
都已經完成了開庭陳詞
in the Moira Queen trial.

134
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:34,770
別理解錯了  但你看起來很惡心
Don't take this the wrong way, but you look disgusting.

135
00:07:34,770 --> 00:07:36,670
好吧  我感覺不太好  費利西蒂
Yeah, well, I don't feel great, Felicity.

136
00:07:37,590 --> 00:07:39,360
你有沒有解決的辦法
Is there a right way to take that?

137
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,010
你應該回家
You should go home.

138
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:42,650
我正要回去
I am going.

139
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:45,980
我只是得安排一個替補保鏢
I just need to make arrangements for a replacement bodyguard.

140
00:07:46,090 --> 00:07:48,430
你打流感疫苗了嗎  我從沒打過
Did you get the flu shot? Personally, I never do.

141
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,260
我知道我應該打
I know that I should.

142
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:51,870
可我  我對針頭很恐懼
I just, I have this thing about needles.

143
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,240
對尖的東西都恐懼
All pointy things, really.

144
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,530
這很諷刺  想想我們跟誰共事
Which is ironic, considering who we work with.

145
00:07:55,530 --> 00:07:57,750
對  不是流感  費利西蒂  更像是
Yeah, it's not the flu, Felicity, it's more like...

146
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,590
狄格
Dig!

147
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:02,590
有人嗎
Hello?

148
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,430
你在這里嗎
Are you here?

149
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:08,250
在這里  在那里
Here...there...

150
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:10,010
在任何地方
Everywhere.

151
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,130
那么
So.

152
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:14,950
我們的科學項目進展如何
How goes our little science project?

153
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,600
如你所料
Working like you said it would.

154
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:17,940
多美妙啊
How wonderful.

155
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,500
是這樣
Ah, so listen.

156
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:23,670
干這事要五萬塊
Doing the thing was 50,000.

157
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,940
保守這個秘密
Keeping quiet about it,

158
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,010
我覺得應該再加五萬
I'm thinking it should be 50 more.

159
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:32,100
不過我想讓流言傳開
Oh, I want word to spread.

160
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:34,780
這正是整體目標的一部分
It's kind of the whole objective, actually.

161
00:08:37,110 --> 00:08:38,400
你懂我意思嗎
You see my point?

162
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:43,430
你應該知道  我覺得事后談判
You should know, I find post hoc negotiation...

163
00:08:43,730 --> 00:08:44,900
很令人討厭
distasteful.

164
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,290
真可惜你看不到你的工作
Such a shame you won't get to see

165
00:08:49,290 --> 00:08:51,260
會得到怎樣的成果  博士
what your works have wrought, doctor.

166
00:08:52,430 --> 00:08:54,530
但很快  所有人都能看到
But soon, everyone else will.

167
00:08:55,730 --> 00:08:59,870
而且他們會祈求它快點結束
And they'll beg for it to end.

168
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,200
你來這里干什么
What the hell are you doing here?

169
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,180
我聽說你昏過去了
I heard you passed out.

170
00:09:12,180 --> 00:09:13,420
我讓費利西蒂別打電話給你
I told Felicity not to call you.

171
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:15,400
對  但在那之前  你喊了一聲就倒下了
Yeah, but before that, you said "Gaw" And "Thud,"

172
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,730
所以我沒把你的話當回事
so I didn't take it very seriously.

173
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:19,290
她打給我是對的  狄格爾  你需要就醫
She was right to call me. Diggle, you need medical attention.

174
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:21,150
他不止需要就醫  狄格昏過去時
He needs more than that. When Dig passed out,

175
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,500
我把他的血樣給了公司里的一個化學家
I sent a sample of his blood to a chemist I know at QC.

176
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,890
他欠我人情  說來話長
The guy owes me a favor. Long story,

177
00:09:24,890 --> 00:09:26,170
我幫他取消過停車罰單
I fixed his parking ticket.

178
00:09:26,170 --> 00:09:28,050
其實也不是很長
Huh. I guess it's not that long.

179
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:30,160
費利西蒂  血樣
Felicity. The blood sample.

