But I returned because you needed my help.

727
00:41:07,560 --> 00:41:08,600
什么幫助
Help?

728
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:10,150
你的庭審
With your trial.

729
00:41:11,430 --> 00:41:12,700
難道你覺得陪審團無緣無故
You didn't think that jury acquitted you

730
00:41:12,700 --> 00:41:14,250
就會宣布你無罪嗎
without a little persuasion?

731
00:41:14,890 --> 00:41:16,070
天哪
Dear god.

732
00:41:19,010 --> 00:41:20,420
你想怎么樣  馬爾科姆
What do you want, Malcolm?

733
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:24,820
我在星城還有勢力
I still have resources in Starling.

734
00:41:25,910 --> 00:41:27,080
人脈
Associates.

735
00:41:29,470 --> 00:41:31,600
在地方檢察官辦公室也有
Including one in the D.A.'s office.

736
00:41:32,830 --> 00:41:35,500
我跟進了唐納先生對你的調查
I followed Mr. Donner's investigation of you with interest.

737
00:41:35,650 --> 00:41:38,260
這么多年你如此輕松地隱瞞我們的事
The ease with which you lied about us for years,

738
