讓我思索你是不是騙了我
it made me wonder whether you lied to me.

739
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:42,880
我沒有
No. No.

740
00:41:43,370 --> 00:41:46,580
我暗地里做了一個小小的親子測試
It was a matter of a simple surreptitious genetics test

741
00:41:46,990 --> 00:41:48,220
證實了我的懷疑
to confirm my suspicion.

742
00:41:48,220 --> 00:41:49,320
別
Don't.

743
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:54,700
猜猜我在發現西婭是我女兒時有多高興
Imagine my joy at learning that Thea is my daughter.

